# Aim Trainer (Pygame)

A simple local aim trainer built with Python + Pygame. Train your mouse aim with random targets, tracking mode, and session stats. This is strictly a standalone training tool â€” not a cheat for multiplayer games.

## Features
- Random target spawns with adjustable size and time limit
- Tracking mode (moving target)
- Hit/miss stats and accuracy
- Session timer and best accuracy saved locally

## Requirements
- Python 3.8+
- pip

## Install
```bash
git clone <this-repo-url>
cd aim-trainer
python -m venv venv
# Windows
venv\Scripts\activate
# macOS/Linux
source venv/bin/activate

pip install -r requirements.txt
